{% markdown %}
Makerspace-Baasrode is opened on every friday for enthousiast that love work or talk about computers, technology and brainstorm about ideas that can be build.
No experience is required!

Be present to experience the fun!


* Location: Hof ten Rode 61, 9200 Baasrode (Dendermonde)
* Site: [www.Makerspace-Baasrode.be](http://www.makerspace-baasrode.be/)
* Slack: [makerspace-baasrode.slack.com](https://makerspace-baasrode.slack.com/)
* Twitter: [twitter.com/MakersBaasrode](https://twitter.com/MakersBaasrode)
* Instagram: [www.instagram.com/makerspacebaasrode/](https://www.instagram.com/makerspacebaasrode/)
* Github: [github.com/Makerspace-baasrode](https://github.com/Makerspace-baasrode)

{% endmarkdown %}
